g.title: ASSERT_ALL_RESETS->RELEASE_PLL_RESET
g.text: (RX_PLL0_USED and not TX_PLL0_USED and (PLL0REFCLKLOST = '0') and pll_reset_asserted = '1') or
(not RX_PLL0_USED and TX_PLL0_USED and (PLL1REFCLKLOST = '0') and pll_reset_asserted = '1') or

g.title: MONITOR_DATA_VALID->ASSERT_ALL_RESETS
g.text: time_out_100us = '1' and data_valid_sync = '0' and DONT_RESET_ON_DATA_ERROR = '0' and reset_time_out = '0'
